#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"Here are some preferences that you may wish to set initially. The full list and "
"explanation of the user preferences are documented in the section :doc:`User "
"Preferences </preferences/index>`."
msgstr ""
"本页介绍一些需要首先配置的用户设置。完整的用户设置列表和解释位于 :doc:`用户设置 "
"</preferences/index>` 章节。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:12
msgid "Language"
msgstr "语言"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:14
msgid ""
"At :menuselection:`File --> User Preferences --> System`, enable *International "
"Fonts* to choose the *Language* and what to translate from *Interface*, "
"*Tooltips* and *New Data*."
msgstr ""
"在 :menuselection:`File(文件) --> User Preferences(用户设置) --> System(系统)`, "
"启用 *International Fonts(国际化字体)* ，选择 *Language(语言)* 与需要翻译的界面内"
"容： *Interface(界面)*, *Tooltips(工具提示)* 和 *New Data(新建数据)* 。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:17
msgid "See :ref:`prefs-system-international` for details."
msgstr "详情参见  :ref:`prefs-system-international` 。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:21
msgid "Input"
msgstr "输入"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:23
msgid ""
"If you have a compact keyboard without a separate number pad, enable :"
"menuselection:`File --> User Preferences --> Emulate Numpad`."
msgstr ""
"如果你用的是紧凑型键盘，没有独立的数字键区域，可以启用 :menuselection:`File(文"
"件) --> User Preferences(用户设置) --> 模拟数字键盘`。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:26
msgid ""
"If you do not have a middle mouse button, you can enable :menuselection:`File --"
"> User Preferences --> Emulate 3 Button Mouse`."
msgstr ""
"如果没有鼠标中键，可以启用 :menuselection:`File(文件) --> User Preferences(用户设"
"置) --> 模拟三键鼠标`。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:29
msgid "See :doc:`Input Preferences </preferences/input>` for details."
msgstr "详情参见 :doc:`输入设置 </preferences/input>` 。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:33
msgid "File and Paths"
msgstr "文件和路径"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:35
msgid ""
"At :menuselection:`File --> User Preferences --> File` you can set options such "
"as what external *Image Editor* to use, such as GIMP or Krita, and the Animation "
"Player."
msgstr ""
"在 :menuselection:`文件 --> 用户设置 --> 文件` 中，可以设置选项如外部图像编辑器为"
"GIMP，Krita，还有动画播放器。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:39
msgid ""
"The :ref:`temp-dir` sets where to store files such as temporary renders and auto-"
"saves."
msgstr ":ref:`temp-dir` 设置用于存储临时渲染结果和自动保存文件的位置。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:43
msgid ""
"The ``//`` at the start of each path in Blender means the directory of the "
"currently opened blend-file, used to reference relative paths."
msgstr ""
"在Blender中路径开头的 ``//``  ，表示当前打开的  ``.blend`` 文件所在目录，用于引用"
"相对路径。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:46
msgid ""
"If you trust the source of your blend-files, you can enable *Auto Run Python "
"Scripts*. This option is meant to protect you from malicious Python scripts that "
"someone can include inside a blend-file. This would not happen by accident, and "
"most users leave this option on to automatically run scripts often used in "
"advanced rigs (such as \"Rigify\" that controls the skeleton of a human rig)."
msgstr ""
"如果信任 ``.blend`` 文件的来源，可以启用 ``自动运行 Python 脚本`` 。该选项是为了"
"保护计算机免受Blender文件中恶意的Python脚本破坏。虽然这并不太常见，大多数用户会选"
"择启用该选项，以自动运行高级绑定中常用到的脚本(如控制角色骨架的 ``Rigify``)。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/introduction.rst:52
msgid "See :doc:`File Preferences </preferences/file>` for details."
msgstr "详情参见 :doc:`文件设置 </preferences/file>` 。"
